Package: filehash
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl3
Description: Command-line file hash calculator
 A simple and efficient command-line tool for calculating file hash values.
 Supports MD5, SHA1, and SHA256 hash algorithms.
 .
 Features:
  - Calculate hash for single or multiple files
  - Support for MD5, SHA1, and SHA256 algorithms
  - Batch processing capability
  - Clean and readable output format
  - Lightweight and fast operation